OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud to start across
OL,6,Fthe midlands. This lifts to leave a
OL,7,Fbright and sunny Sunday for most
OL,8,Fplaces. Isolated showers in Cornwall
OL,9,Fand northern Scotland where it'll be
OL,10,Fcloudier. Staying warm for most.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying cloudy for Northern
OL,13,FIreland and northern Scotland with the
OL,14,Fodd shower, mostly around coasts. Dry
OL,15,Fand clear elsewhere and staying mild
OL,16,Fthrough the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
