OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FTo start the week, patchy
OL,6,Fcloud develops across central and
OL,7,Feastern areas as showers continue for
OL,8,Fnorthern Scotland and Northern
OL,9,FIreland. Sunny in the southwest.
OL,10,FFeeling warm in the sun.
